The Municipal Accountant should see to it that no additional cash advances are granted to any AO until such time that his/her cash advances are duly liquidated; and
The Municipal Mayor thru the Municipal Accountant see to it that the prohibition of transferring cash advances between one AO to another should be strictly enforced.

